    <item>
      <title>Docs: Getting Started</title>
      <link>/docs/getting-started/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/docs/getting-started/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h2 id=&#34;system-requirements&#34;&gt;System requirements&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;macOS 11 Big Sur or later&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;installation&#34;&gt;Installation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Download dmg file from &lt;a href=&#34;/&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open a downloaded dmg file.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Move TrueWidget.app into Applications.

    
    
    
      
    
    
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img
        src=&#34;/docs/getting-started/images/install@2x.png&#34;
        alt=&#34;install@2x.png&#34;
        style=&#34;width: 660px&#34;
      /&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open TrueWidget from Launchpad.

    
    
    
      
    
    
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img
        src=&#34;/docs/getting-started/images/launchpad@2x.png&#34;
        alt=&#34;launchpad@2x.png&#34;
        style=&#34;width: 843px&#34;
      /&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A menu bar icon will be added and the application window will appear.

    
    
    
      
    
    
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img
        src=&#34;/docs/getting-started/images/menu@2x.png&#34;
        alt=&#34;menu@2x.png&#34;
        style=&#34;width: 442px&#34;
      /&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;


    
    
    
      
    
    
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img
        src=&#34;/docs/getting-started/images/widget@2x.png&#34;
        alt=&#34;widget@2x.png&#34;
        style=&#34;width: 266px&#34;
      /&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;whats-next&#34;&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s next?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../configuration&#34;&gt;Configuration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Docs: How to quit TrueWidget</title>
      <link>/docs/help/quit/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/docs/help/quit/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;TrueWidget keeps running in the background even if you close the Settings window.&lt;br /&gt;
To quit TrueWidget, choose &amp;ldquo;Quit TrueWidget&amp;rdquo; from the menu bar.&lt;/p&gt;




  


&lt;figure&gt;
  &lt;img
    src=&#34;/docs/help/quit/images/menu-quit@2x.png&#34;
    alt=&#34;menu-quit@2x.png&#34;
    style=&#34;width: 313px&#34;
  /&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;



&lt;div class=&#34;alert alert-primary&#34; role=&#34;alert&#34;&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&#34;alert-heading&#34;&gt;Note&lt;/h4&gt;

    &lt;p&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;ve hidden the menu bar icon, you can also quit TrueWidget from Settings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../../configuration/open-settingsoc/&#34;&gt;Open Settings&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Press &lt;code&gt;Quit TrueWidget&lt;/code&gt; button.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure&gt;
  &lt;img
    src=&#34;/docs/help/quit/images/quit@2x.png&#34;
    alt=&#34;quit@2x.png&#34;
    style=&#34;width: 800px&#34;
  /&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;/div&gt;


      </description>
    </item>
    
